entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have contacted Sarlis about a corporate espionage mission. This looks like it might pay very well.
entries.journal_entry_description: A new contact has surfaced. Your network is expanding. Go find out what this mission has in store for you.
entries.task00_comm_message_text: I have another job for you. This one is corporate. I am familiar with the corporation initiating the mission and they pay very well. Kaesii says you need to meet Sarlis in Mos Entha. Here is the location for the meeting.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Lercer has contacted you again about a mission. Kaesii has found out about a corporate espionage mishap. She has asked Lercer to get in touch with you.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: You need to meet your contact in Mos Entha. Don't waste too much time, this looks like a good payoff and it's time critical.
